ss=\"card-title pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>\n                            計程車</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showText\">約10分鐘\n<br>費用：120左右\n<br>缺點：有時短程司機不載or價格會超出100&nbsp;<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"card p-3 col-12 col-md-6\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 3\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-3': cardsAmount == '4',\n                             'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper media-container-row\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>\n                            高鐵</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showText\">1. 搭到台中站→轉台鐵新烏日站→台中火車站(10分鐘)\n<br>2. 搭接駁車至科博館站或土庫停車場站，再改搭計程車至民權路求真大門\n<br>費用：15元<br>(高鐵票錢不算)&nbsp;<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
