          "_name": "features12",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"features12\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Icons\" name=\"showIcons\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Media Size\" name=\"mediaSize\" min=\"10\" max=\"60\" step=\"1\" value=\"60\">\n        <select title=\"Cards\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">4</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/1397140361-2633628054_waifu2x_photo_noise3_scale_tta-1760x1320.png\" selected parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#f9f9f9\">\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title pb-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n            美食大特搜</h2>\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">早餐 介紹&amp;特別推薦 位置</h3>\n\n        <div class=\"media-container-row pt-5\">\n            <div class=\"block-content align-right\">\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                             <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-upload mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\"></h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>                \n\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\">(e)5.永和豆漿 <br>供應早餐、宵夜。（Time：PM17:00~AM10:00 <br>禮拜六公休）\n<br>(f)6.東方美 <br>提供選擇多樣<br>好吃推推。\n<br>(g)7.STOP新美食<br>早餐、早午餐 <br>（Time：~PM14:00）\n<br>8.apple 簡餐<br>好吃\n<br>9.阿寶 <br>各種早餐\n<br>.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-drag-n-drop2 mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\">\n                                Easy and Simple to Use\n                            </h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\">\n                            Just drop the blocks into the page, edit content inline and publish - no technical skills required.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-figure\" mbr-style=\"{'width': mediaSize + '%'}\">\n                <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/pic-heaven_hand_waifu2x_photo_noise3_scale_tta_1%20(1)-778x511.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"block-content align-left  \">\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                             <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-features mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\"></h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>                \n\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\">(a)1.嚕嚕米 <br>好吃！<br>推薦薯泥雞排吐司、<br>泡菜蛋餅\n<br>(b)2.早安美芝城 <br>好吃～人很多喔！<br>（推薦薯泥吐司！）\n<br>(c)3.拉亞漢堡 <br>特推匈牙利辣雞芝加哥蛋堡！<br>（Time：AM7:00~11:00）\n<br>(d)4.美味廚房 <br>供應早餐、早午餐。<br>套餐都會附一杯飲料。（Time：AM6:00~PM15:00）&nbsp;<br></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"card pl-3 pr-3 pb-5\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-card-img-title\">\n                        <div class=\"card-img pb-3\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbri-sites mbr-iconfont\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-crt-title\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-crt-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-crt-title\">\n                                Unlimited Sites\n                            </h4>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\">\n                            Mobirise gives you the freedom to develop as many websites as you like given the fact that it is a desktop app.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
